time to attack that BACK!👏 how often do you train your back? I’m training back 2 times per week & loveee it! 
exercises shown:
1️⃣ single arm row | 3 x 10 - 12 per side
2️⃣ v grip pulldown | 3 x 12
3️⃣ barbell row | 4 x 6 - 8
4️⃣ straight arm pulldown | 3 x 12 - 15

double tap ❤️ to show some love! Let’s do this!💪 #workout #fitness #workoutroutine #workoutvideo #backworkout #fit

node.text:
shoulders + back. my two favs😌 sooo for this workout I didn’t count reps, but picked a weight I knew I could probably do 12ish reps with. go till (mental) failure & then DIG DEEPER. you can always do 2 more reps🔥 did you ever not count reps?🙃

3 sets per exercise and it was fireee! exercises shown: 
1 seated shoulder press 
2 face pulls 
3 seated lateral raises 
4 straight arm pulldown
5 lat pulldown

#gymmotivation #workout #training #workoutmotivation

workout 
RDL 3 x 10-12 (go sloooow)
hex bar deadlifts 3 x 12
superset sumo squat x split squat 3 x 10-12 (per side) per exercise 
standing leg curl 3 x 12 per side 

#workout #legday #gymmotivation #workoutmotivation
